<!doctype html><html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"><title>Ed Hatrick Smith - Wardrobe World project</title><meta name="description" content="Ed Hatrick-Smith: Wardrobe World project "/><meta name="keywords" content="web developer, desginer, photographer, awesome person, solutions"/><meta name="author" content="Edward Hatrick-Smith: ed.hatricksmith@gmail.com"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.projects.min.css"/><?php $thisPage="work";?><?php include_once("/home/akolob/public_html/analyticstracking.php") ?></head><body><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/header.php");?><div id="projects"><h1 class="works_heading">Wardrobe World</h1><p class="breadcrumbs"><em><a href="/work/work.php">Work</a> / Wardrobe World</em></p><article><p class="projects_first">Wardrobe World is one of New Zealand's premiere fitted wardrobe, kitchen and storage solution manufacturers. They distribute nationally to 21 different regions and are happily thriving.</p><p>The site was written in <span class="small-cap">html / css</span> and features a sprinkling of jQuery. One of the more technically complex features are the <span class="small-cap">php</span> forms which have some custom scripts to direct the message to the relevant regional distributors.</p><p>This is one of the first large design and developement jobs I produced for <a href="http://www.carbonstudios.co.nz/" target="_blank">Carbon Studios</a>. In fact the build is probably at least a year old and the design is significantly more than that. While I still like the project, my design skills have progressed and <span class="small-cap">html5 / css3</span> has transformed the way sites are built. It all changes so quickly.</p></article><section><h2 class="works_heading">Project Images</h2><div id="container" class="project_width"><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/wardrobe/image_01_lge.jpg"><div id="project_lg" class="project"><img src="/images/works/projects/wardrobe/image_01_sml.jpg" alt="Wardrobe World home page"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/wardrobe/image_02_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/wardrobe/image_02_sml.jpg" alt="Wardrobe kitchens page"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/wardrobe/image_03_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/wardrobe/image_03_sml.jpg" alt="Wardrobe World form page"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a></div><div class="clearfix"></div></section><ul><li><a href="http://www.wardrobeworld.co.nz" target="_blank">Visit Website</a></li></ul></div><div class="clearfix"></div><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/footer.php");?><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.projects.min.js" ></script><script type="text/javascript">$(".fancybox") .attr('rel', 'gallery') .fancybox({padding : 0 ,minWidth : 215 ,maxWidth : 900 ,autoSize : true ,maxHeight : 600 ,});</script><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.isotope-min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){var $container=$('#container');$container.isotope({itemSelector: '.project'});});</script></body></html>